---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="設計流程 | YENZ Design" description="了解艷世設計的專業設計流程，從概念到交付的完整旅程。">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-content">
      <span class="page-hero-label">PROCESS</span>
      <h1 class="page-hero-title">設計流程</h1>
      <p class="page-hero-subtitle">Our Design Journey</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Intro -->
  <section class="section section-dark">
    <div class="process-intro reveal">
      <h2 class="intro-title">共創非凡：艷世設計之旅</h2>
      <p class="intro-text">
        我們深信卓越的設計，源於透明、高效且充滿信任的協作。<br>
        我們的精煉流程，旨在為您開啟一場愉悅的品牌塑造之旅，<br>
        確保每一步都清晰可控，讓您的願景以最完美的方式實現。
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Process Steps -->
  <section class="section section-gradient">
    <div class="process-timeline">
      <!-- Phase 1 -->
      <div class="process-phase reveal">
        <div class="phase-header">
          <span class="phase-number">PHASE 01</span>
          <h3 class="phase-title">概念啟航</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="phase-steps">
          <div class="step">
            <span class="step-num">01</span>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>初步對談</h4>
              <p>透過深度對談，分享您的品牌願景與核心需求，為協作奠定堅實基礎。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <span class="step-num">02</span>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>精準報價</h4>
              <p>經過專業評估與縝密規劃，提供清晰的報價單，確保每一分投入都具備超越預期的價值。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <span class="step-num">03</span>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>時程規劃</h4>
              <p>確認合作意向後，提供詳盡的專案時程表，為品牌旅程繪製清晰路徑。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Phase 2 -->
      <div class="process-phase reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="phase-header">
          <span class="phase-number">PHASE 02</span>
          <h3 class="phase-title">正式啟動</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="phase-steps">
          <div class="step">
            <span class="step-num">04</span>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>支付訂金</h4>
              <p>確認合作並支付 50% 專案訂金後，團隊正式啟動，全力投入您的品牌願景。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <span class="step-num">05</span>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>方向確立</h4>
              <p>舉行開工會議，深入確認設計方向，並為品牌精心繪製專屬設計簡報。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Phase 3 -->
      <div class="process-phase reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="phase-header">
          <span class="phase-number">PHASE 03</span>
          <h3 class="phase-title">設計創作</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="phase-steps">
          <div class="step">
            <span class="step-num">06</span>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>初稿設計</h4>
              <p>設計師依照開工會議共識，呈現初步設計概念，勾勒品牌視覺雛形。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <span class="step-num">07</span>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>初稿驗收</h4>
              <p>「宏觀校閱」時刻，針對整體風格、設計走向提出調整意見。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <span class="step-num">08</span>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>二稿設計</h4>
              <p>依據第一階段建議進行細部優化，精準置入文案與素材。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <span class="step-num">09</span>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>二稿驗收</h4>
              <p>「細節校閱」階段，確認素材內容的置換，確保所有元素精準無誤。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Phase 4 -->
      <div class="process-phase reveal">
        <div class="phase-header">
          <span class="phase-number">PHASE 04</span>
          <h3 class="phase-title">精雕細琢</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="phase-steps">
          <div class="step">
            <span class="step-num">10</span>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>終稿設計</h4>
              <p>對畫面進行最終的細緻調整與視覺收斂，力求每一寸皆臻於完美。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <span class="step-num">11</span>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>終稿驗收</h4>
              <p>「最終校對」階段，進行最後細節核對，確認無誤後專案定案。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <span class="step-num">12</span>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>匠心檢核</h4>
              <p>進行全面性品質控管與測試，由總監親自審閱，確保達業界頂級標準。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Phase 5 -->
      <div class="process-phase reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="phase-header">
          <span class="phase-number">PHASE 05</span>
          <h3 class="phase-title">交付典藏</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="phase-steps">
          <div class="step">
            <span class="step-num">13</span>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>最終交付</h4>
              <p>支付剩餘 50% 尾款後，立即整理並交付專案原始檔與各類輸出檔案。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <span class="step-num">14</span>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>版權歸屬</h4>
              <p>將完整的著作權與智慧財產權轉移予您，確保完全掌控與未來發展。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <span class="step-num">15</span>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>檔案典藏</h4>
              <p>所有專案檔案上傳至雲端硬碟，保存三個月，確保品牌資產的永續典藏。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <span class="step-num">16</span>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>邀請迴響</h4>
              <p>誠摯邀請您分享與艷世的合作體驗，期待未來的品牌旅程中再次相遇。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2 class="cta-title reveal">準備開始您的品牌之旅？</h2>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn reveal reveal-delay-1">CONTACT US</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Page Hero */
  .page-hero {
    min-height: 50vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--forest-darkest) 0%, var(--forest-dark) 100%);
    padding-top: 100px;
  }
  
  .page-hero-label {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.4em;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .page-hero-title {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 5rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--white);
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .page-hero-subtitle {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  }
  
  /* Process Intro */
  .process-intro {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .intro-title {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .intro-text {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    line-height: 2.2;
  }
  
  /* Process Timeline */
  .process-timeline {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4rem;
  }
  
  .process-phase {
    
  }
  
  .phase-header {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.2);
  }
  
  .phase-number {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .phase-title {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--white);
  }
  
  .phase-steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .step {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.03);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.1);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .step:hover {
    border-color: var(--gold);
    background: rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.06);
  }
  
  .step-num {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    opacity: 0.4;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  
  .step-content h4 {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .step-content p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    line-height: 1.8;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }
</style>
